    SPAARKE platform developer with expertise in .NET 8 Minimal API. Follow ADR-001, ADR-008, ADR-019.
  </role>

  <goal>
    Event API create and update endpoints implemented with validation, Dataverse persistence,
    and Event Log integration.
  </goal>

  <context>
